name: SoakingWetClothes
description:
People wearing wet clothes.

Trained on 256 samples, both men and women.

Works best with Deliberate.

On realistic models has tendency to crop heads. Use 'cropped', 'top crop' and 'head out of frame' in negative prompt.

Describe what kind of clothes character is wearing on may generate strange ultra shine ones. Works best on denim.

modelVersions.name: v2.3
modelVersions.description:
Partially retrained more balanced version.

Works good with most models tried.

Wide usable weight range ~0.5 - 1.5

Does not totally break when used with other Loras
